dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.body:
Attention Google: 

Further to our previous Urgent Notices of Copyright Infringement, I am writing on behalf of Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation and/or its subsidiaries and affiliated companies ("Fox"), to notify you of the continued infringement of Fox's intellectual property rights in the titles identified in this email in Google search results.  Notices of Copyright Infringement were previously sent to Google for the identified titles and links on the dates listed in this email.

Fox repeats our demand that Google take immediate action to stop such infringements.

The search results and links identified in this email are specific examples of Google search results linking to video files, images, artwork, and/or websites that infringe upon Fox's intellectual property rights.

Fox hereby repeats its demand that Google promptly remove and disable the links to all unauthorized copies of works whose copyrights are owned by Fox of which it is aware, including the infringing files identified in this email. 

This letter is not a complete statement of Fox's rights in connection with this matter, and nothing contained herein constitutes an express or implied waiver of any rights, remedies, or defenses of Fox in connection with this matter, all of which are expressly reserved. 

The undersigned has a good faith belief that use of the materials in the manner described herein is not authorized by Fox, its agent, or the law. The information in this notice is accurate. Under penalty of perjury, the undersigned is authorized to act on behalf of Fox with respect to this matter.


Sincerely,
MiMTiD Corp.
[redacted]
Managing Director
[redacted]
[redacted]mimtid.com

Please note as of November 13th, 2010 includes Video Files, Images, Artwork, and/or Websites.
